  "metadata": {
    "name": "Verify that Interactive Boot is Disabled",
    "description": "{{{ full_name }}} systems support an \"interactive boot\" option that can\nbe used to prevent services from being started. On a {{{ full_name }}}\nsystem, interactive boot can be enabled by providing a <tt>1</tt>,\n<tt>yes</tt>, <tt>true</tt>, or <tt>on</tt> value to the\n<tt>systemd.confirm_spawn</tt> kernel argument.",
    "rationale": "Using interactive boot, the console user could disable auditing, firewalls,\nor other services, weakening system security.",
